MÔ TẢ CÔNG VIỆC

We are looking for Mobile Developer to join our team. This position offers an inspirational space to create the next innovation in mobile applications.

- Build the leading edge Android product and make impact on a large user base, work with a great international team and more; 

- Work and collaborate in an agile environment with Technical Lead, Product Lead, Backend team and UX for accelerating product delivery; 

- Be actively involved in product discussions; 

- Strongly contribute to the mobile development process and technical knowledge of the entire organization.

YÊU CẦU ỨNG VIÊN

Fresher Android Developer

Broad knowledge and experience in: 

- Java language; 

- Object-oriented programming (OOP); 

- Data Structure and Algorithms; 

- Networking; 

Android Developer 

Broad knowledge and experience in: 

- Android development (1 year or more); 

- Android SDK, JSON, GIT, REST; 

- Native App Designing Experience: Knowledge of UI elements & layout, basic animation technique (big plus if you have experience in mobile UI/UX);

QUYỀN LỢI ĐƯỢC HƯỞNG
– Attractive salary: Upto $2000, 13th month salary;
– Private health insurance coverage (Generali insurance);
– Flexible working time;
– Dynamic and youthful working environment;
– Cool and modern working space;
– Chances to build high impact products, operate in full continuous-integration software development setup with the latest and popular technology stacks in an open-minded, transparent and agile environment;
– Training courses & talks with talented tech professionals covering a wide range of topics to cultivate your skills;
– Annual summer vacation, Teambuilding activities;
– Happy hours, Game, Football, Book Club.
CÁCH THỨC ỨNG TUYỂN

